# (PR https://github.com/Kludex/python-multipart/pull/290), released as 0.0.30.
# Drops the cosmetic CHANGELOG.md hunk; keeps the 4 functional hunks in
# python_multipart/multipart.py and the renamed/rewritten regression test.
